WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.170 --> 00:00:08.040
Today well be reviewing the Croozer Dog Carrier
Bike Trailer and Stroller part number CZ00111401.

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:11.470
This carrier is able to carry dogs up to 99
lbs.

00:00:11.470 --> 00:00:16.070
This versatile dog carrier and bike trailer
lets you take your large dog with you so he

00:00:16.070 --> 00:00:18.870
doesnt miss the outdoor fun.

00:00:18.870 --> 00:00:24.260
The dog carrier converts for either strolling
or biking with your dog.

00:00:24.260 --> 00:00:28.430
Its heavy duty plastic wheel slides into the
center bracket on the front of the carrier

00:00:28.430 --> 00:00:38.430
to create a dog stroller.

00:00:38.430 --> 00:00:46.719
The hitch arm and axle mount let you create
a bike trailer.

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:52.420
The hitch works on bikes with quick release
skewers and solid axle hubs.

00:00:52.420 --> 00:00:56.850
The large entry and exit doors make it easy
for your dog to get in and out.

00:00:56.850 --> 00:01:02.749
Both doors do zip close to secure your pet.

00:01:02.749 --> 00:01:06.970
The front door has a clear plastic rain cover.

00:01:06.970 --> 00:01:12.100
The sturdy steel chassis forms a protective
roll cage and the mesh side windows provider

00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:57.149
better air flow 

00:01:57.149 --> 00:02:02.759
on warm days.

